## Context Sharing Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant Caller
  participant Broker as ContextBroker (GenServer)
  participant ParentServer as AgentServer (parent)
  participant ChildServer as AgentServer (child)
  participant MemCtx as MemoryContext
  participant DB as Postgres

  Note over Caller: share_context/5 — parent → child
  Caller->>Broker: share_context(parent_agent, parent_session_id, child_agent, child_session_id, scope)
  Broker->>Broker: ContextScope.new(scope)
  Broker->>ParentServer: session_context(parent_agent, parent_session_id)
  ParentServer-->>Broker: {:ok, %Context{workspace, memory, inherited, local}}
  Broker->>Broker: validate_max_depth(context, scope)
  Broker->>Broker: build_shared_payload(context, scope)
  Broker->>ChildServer: merge_inherited_context(child_agent, child_session_id, from_session_id, payload)
  ChildServer-->>Broker: {:ok, child_context}
  Broker->>DB: INSERT agent_context_shares (from, to, scope, delta)
  Broker-->>Caller: {:ok, child_context, share_record}

  Note over Caller: promote_delta/3 — child → parent
  Caller->>Broker: promote_delta(parent_agent, parent_session_id, delta)
  Broker->>Broker: ContextDelta.new(delta)
  alt delta.promote == true
    Broker->>ParentServer: apply_delta(parent_agent, parent_session_id, delta)
    ParentServer-->>Broker: {:ok, updated_context}
    Broker->>MemCtx: append_memory(agent_id, memory_type, content, ...)
    MemCtx->>DB: INSERT agent_memories
    Broker->>DB: INSERT agent_context_shares (child→parent, delta)
    Broker-->>Caller: {:ok, promoted_context, memories, share_record}
  else delta.promote == false
    Broker-->>Caller: {:ok, :skipped}
  end
```

